{"tid":1826070,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"【集思廣益】一人一個影快相雷射槍例位","createTime":"2020-01-15T23:59:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T04:16:58.000Z","uid":149188,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7bdc34fd4be8b77dd0ee67a7a5c88ac552d38281","tid":1826070,"uid":149188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T23:59:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府呢排太有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再比無謂錢佢地賺</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n1. <strong>觀塘繞道</strong>隔音屏來回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. <strong>黃竹坑道</strong>往香港仔上橋位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. <strong>清水灣道</strong>落西貢 - 突然轉50<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"578bc646fd39d14b5c984453bdf833bf47d6d973","tid":1826070,"uid":162008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T00:05:43.000Z","msg":"台灣就公投完啦 咁香港人呢？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人唔可以再慣性沉默</span></span>，<br />\n一起發聲，習慣投票表達意見吧<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票 ~ 一個香港人的投票應用程式<br />\n下載連結：iOS / Android<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkvote.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkvote.org&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GGVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=465112e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkvote.org</a><br />\n<br />\n原post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1821362/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1821362/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"377d35513728e2a9b062e1ac504a9c3fb8fa0ce9","tid":1826070,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T00:28:22.000Z","msg":"睇app"},{"pid":"03e65ac932a637b3803759e1c9ffd044fddaa0f8","tid":1826070,"uid":28258,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T00:44:35.000Z","msg":"港島：<br />\n東廊東行柯達大廈<br />\n永泰道柴灣工業城<br />\n干諾道中西行美銀<br />\n黃竹坑道香港仔工業學校<br />\n香隧灣仔入口<br />\n<br />\n九龍：<br />\n渡船街東莞街美孚<br />\n浸會橋尖沙咀<br />\n老龍天馬苑觀塘<br />\n老龍斧山道泳池<br />\n觀塘時光隧道來回<br />\n觀繞麗港城油塘<br />\n<br />\n新畀：<br />\n荔橋瑪嘉烈美孚<br />\n3號仔華潤向青衣<br />\n3號仔4號碼頭青衣<br />\n3號仔南昌村尖沙咀<br />\n8號碼頭昂橋<br />\n昂橋青衣南50彎位來回<br />\n<br />\n歡迎接龍"},{"pid":"c2ba0720ed684c6771b5ae5dd91fc149ac02f998","tid":1826070,"uid":225192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T00:53:45.000Z","msg":"馬騮山出九龍"},{"pid":"e6d91168b37e2b22a70790e165aba5014a52df7e","tid":1826070,"uid":9496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T01:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6bc062322e4e8da42a2be12e0000fa2860234c","tid":1826070,"uid":28258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6d91168b37e2b22a70790e165aba5014a52df7e","tid":1826070,"uid":9496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T01:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T04:41:11.000Z","msg":"Weekend就會出動<br />\n頭先出左長青隧道，過左青衣會合位都好多狗車，可能有快相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6db5c5acd44cb3e0753b85e23dfbb3b2fc06cb75","tid":1826070,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"377d35513728e2a9b062e1ac504a9c3fb8fa0ce9","tid":1826070,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T00:28:22.000Z","msg":"睇app"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T04:52:12.000Z","msg":"咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1969650663ab96adbc91336684288a33cdf2521","tid":1826070,"uid":227404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2ba0720ed684c6771b5ae5dd91fc149ac02f998","tid":1826070,"uid":225192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc